msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_ALCHEMY_FIREWORKER_ASHES"
msgstr "Behind the alchemy room of {sect_name}, a fireworker sifted pale furnace ash again and again, afraid to miss any powder that could still be returned to the furnace."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_APPRAISER_AVATAR_SELL_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left the consignment house in {region_name}, the appraiser held the item under the lamp three more times before letting the bookkeeper record it."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_BLACK_MARKET_BROKER_HIDDEN_MAP"
msgstr "In a back alley of {region_name}, a black-market broker kept a torn sea chart under his sleeve and said the reef shadow on it appeared only once every thirty years."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_DOCK_LABORER_NIGHT_CARGO"
msgstr "As the night tide rose at {region_name}, several dock laborers dragged soaked sea-beast hides into the salt warehouse."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_FERRYMAN_MOVE_REGION_ECHO"
msgstr "At the ferry in {region_name}, the tide guide studied the water and warned {avatar_name} that fewer travelers dared cross at night lately."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_GRAIN_KEEPER_GOVERN_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} finished handling city affairs in {region_name}, the granary keeper added a line beside the accounts, and the voices outside the gate softened."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HEALER_HELP_PEOPLE_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left {region_name}, the clinic doctor sent the remaining wound powder to the porridge shed, where several displaced people thanked them in low voices."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HERB_VENDOR_AVATAR_BUY_ECHO"
msgstr "While {avatar_name} chose spirit materials in {region_name}, the medicine shop assistant wiped the counter again and again, never daring to hurry them."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HERB_VENDOR_MARKET_ARGUMENT"
msgstr "In {region_name}, a herb vendor and a gatherer argued for half a day over the age of a bundle of herbs before a shop assistant fetched the keeper to inspect it."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_IMMORTAL_PARENT_WAITS"
msgstr "Outside the gate of {sect_name}, parents seeking immortality waited with their child until the sun slanted west; the gate child brought water but promised no message."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MARKET_REACTS_TO_YAO"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} passed through the market in {region_name}, several stallholders lowered their calls, and a woman drew her child behind her."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MEDICINE_ASSISTANT_AVATAR_INQUIRY"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} asked prices in a medicine shop in {region_name}, the assistant hurriedly pushed aside several mortal herbs and set out only goods that still held spiritual energy."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MINE_SURVIVOR_WHISPERS"
msgstr "Beside a tea shed in {region_name}, a mine survivor whispered that knocking sounds came from deep underground at night; none of the listeners answered."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MOUNTAIN_GUARD_AVATAR_WARNING"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} passed the mountain gate of {region_name}, a guard gathered his courage to warn that strange winds often rose ahead at night, then lowered his head and stepped back."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MOUNTAIN_GUARD_WATCHES_CLOUD"
msgstr "A mountain pass guard at {region_name} found a new scorch mark on the wall and looked toward the misty heights, but did not write it into the night watch book."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PATROL_FEARS_EVIL_AVATAR"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left the alleys of {region_name}, a street patrol runner stood by the well for a long while, then simply closed that page of the case book."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PATROL_PLUNDER_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left {region_name}, no lamps were lit in the west alley all night, and even the street patrol runner walked past with lighter steps."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PATROL_RUNNER_CITY_ORDER"
msgstr "At an alley mouth in {region_name}, a street patrol runner waited until two cultivators had gone far away before urging the watching crowd to disperse."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SCRIPTURE_COPYIST_AVATAR_SILENCE"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} passed a side room of the scripture library of {sect_name}, the copyist immediately stilled the brush and resumed writing only after the rustle of robes faded."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SCRIPTURE_COPYIST_WET_PAGES"
msgstr "In a side room of the scripture library of {sect_name}, a copyist spread damp pages over bamboo screens and warned a child not to let inner disciples see them."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_BUYER_MARKET_LIST"
msgstr "At the stalls below {sect_name}, a sect buyer checked the procurement list again, separating grain, charcoal, and medicine bowls while frowning at the price of spirit materials."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_ERRAND_MISSION_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} handed in the sect errand, an outer sect servant folded the procurement list again and quietly let out a breath."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_FIELD_FARMER_AVATAR_PATH"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} passed the field path of {sect_name}, a field farmer stopped hoeing and stepped aside on the ridge, returning to the weeds only after the footsteps faded."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_FIELD_FARMER_LEAF_SPOTS"
msgstr "Beside the spirit fields of {sect_name}, a field farmer found blackened tips on a row of herbs, set down the water bucket, and hurried to find a steward."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_GATE_CHILD_AVATAR_QUESTION"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} passed the gate of {sect_name}, the gate child softly asked whether a message should be sent to the outer court, then immediately lowered his eyes to the steps."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_GATE_CHILD_WAITING"
msgstr "Outside the gate of {sect_name}, a gate child leaned a broom against the stone steps and watched several families seeking immortality slowly leave the morning mist."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_SERVANT_REACTS_TO_DISCIPLE"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} went downhill to buy supplies, an outer sect servant stepped aside by the stone stairs and waited before lifting the rice sacks again."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_TENANT_GRAIN_CART"
msgstr "At the foot of {sect_name}, tenant farmers stopped their grain cart outside the stone steps and quietly counted this year's rent grain while waiting for the steward."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_STORE_REACTS_TO_HIGH_REALM"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} paused before the medicine shop in {region_name}, the keeper immediately had the assistants put away the mortal herbs and set out jade boxes of spirit materials."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_STORYTELLER_RUMOR_TEAHOUSE"
msgstr "In a teahouse in {region_name}, a storyteller claimed an immortal estate had surfaced in the eastern sea; the listeners cheered, while the bookkeeper only noted three more pots of tea sold."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_TEA_SHED_ELDER_AVATAR_PAUSE"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} paused before a tea shed in {region_name}, the elder swallowed the immortal-sect anecdote he had been telling and asked instead whether they wanted more tea."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_TIDE_GUIDE_WARNS_TIDE"
msgstr "The tide at {region_name} suddenly grew rough, and a tide guide advised several small boats to delay sailing while the captains studied the clouds."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_YAMEN_CLERK_LATE_RECORDS"
msgstr "A yamen clerk in {region_name} recopied case files late into the night, lightly passing over the statements involving cultivators and adding only a small note in the corner."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_YAMEN_REACTS_TO_OFFICIAL"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} entered {region_name}, street patrols saluted from afar, and the yamen clerk recopied the piled-up case files overnight."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HUNTER_FOREST_SNARE"
msgstr "At the forest edge of {region_name}, a hunter gathered a dew-soaked snare and found the hoofprints ending before a blue stone."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HERB_GATHERER_MIST_BASKET"
msgstr "Before the mist cleared in {region_name}, a herb gatherer tipped aside half a basket of common plants and kept only a few spirit-lit leaves."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_FERRYMAN_RIVER_ROPE"
msgstr "At the ferry of {region_name}, the river suddenly quieted; the ferryman retied the rope and told travelers not to ask about the return trip."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_CARAVAN_MERCHANT_ROADSIDE_ACCOUNT"
msgstr "Beside the road in {region_name}, traveling merchants entered beast bones, salt sacks, and spirit-material scraps into separate accounts."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_POSTAL_COURIER_LATE_SEAL"
msgstr "The post house lamps in {region_name} stayed lit as a courier hid an urgent letter with cracked seal wax in his sleeve."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_INNKEEPER_ROOM_SCREEN"
msgstr "In an inn at {region_name}, the keeper had the innermost screen cleaned, saying cultivators disliked too much mortal dust."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_BLACKSMITH_SPARK_TALISMAN"
msgstr "Blue-white sparks leapt from the forge in {region_name}; the blacksmith watched a moment, then pinned an old talisman beneath the anvil."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_ARTIFACT_SHOPKEEPER_SEALED_SHELF"
msgstr "The artifact shopkeeper in {region_name} resealed the highest shelf and warned the assistant not to let mortal customers touch it."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PAWNSHOP_CLERK_OLD_TOKEN"
msgstr "In {region_name}, a pawnshop appraiser found half a jade token in an old box and closed the ledger after seeing its broken pattern."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_TAX_COLLECTOR_DAWN_SCALES"
msgstr "At the first dawn drum in {region_name}, a tax collector weighed rice sacks by the gate, then quietly weighed a packet of spirit sand."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_CONSTABLE_CASE_THREAD"
msgstr "At the case table in {region_name}, a constable moved several red strings so they avoided every wooden tag bearing a cultivator name."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_NIGHT_WATCHMAN_THIRD_WATCH"
msgstr "After the third-watch clapper in {region_name}, the night watchman heard robes above the tiles and did not dare look up."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HOUSEHOLD_CLERK_RED_INK"
msgstr "In {region_name}, a registry clerk circled several moved households in red ink and wrote, \"possibly followed an immortal gate.\""

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_NOTICE_CRIER_NEW_EDICT"
msgstr "A notice crier in {region_name} posted a new court proclamation and lowered his voice at \"offerings to immortal gates.\""

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_IMPERIAL_COURIER_DUSTY_CASE"
msgstr "In {region_name}, an imperial courier delivered only the most urgent letter to the yamen and left the rest strapped behind the saddle."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PALACE_ATTENDANT_OUTER_RUMOR"
msgstr "In the rear seats of a teahouse in {region_name}, a palace attendant mentioned changed incense tables in the capital, and the listeners fell silent."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_CENSOR_RETAINER_QUIET_INQUIRY"
msgstr "At the end of an alley in {region_name}, a censor's retainer asked about recent cultivators and left only a cold copper coin."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SHIPWRIGHT_KEEL_MARK"
msgstr "In the shipyard of {region_name}, a shipwright found a thin water pattern on a new keel and told the apprentice to hold the nails."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SALT_STEWARD_WET_LEDGER"
msgstr "The salt warehouse steward in {region_name} opened a damp ledger and recorded several salt losses as \"tide damage.\""

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_FISHERMAN_RED_TIDE_NET"
msgstr "Outside the harbor of {region_name}, a fisherman hauled in a red-stained net and dared not take home the shining scale caught at the bottom."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PEARL_DIVER_SHELL_WHISPER"
msgstr "A pearl diver in {region_name} held an empty shell to the ear, heard something chanting through water, and went pale."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_CHART_PEDDLER_HIDDEN_REEF"
msgstr "A chart peddler in {region_name} darkened the mark for a hidden reef, then told a buyer it was best to forget that route."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PORT_TAX_COLLECTOR_CARGO_MARK"
msgstr "At {region_name}, the port tax collector stamped a cargo crate, saw spirit light leak from the seam, and added another seal."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SHIP_CAPTAIN_STORM_OATH"
msgstr "At {region_name}, the ship captain poured wine into the sea and swore not to chase the contrary tide tonight; no sailor objected."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_POST_STATION_MASTER_TIRED_HORSE"
msgstr "At {region_name}, the post station master touched a sweaty relay horse and turned the next-route tablet over, signaling a longer wait."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MINE_FOREMAN_CRACKED_BEAM"
msgstr "In {region_name}, a mine foreman found a fresh crack in a support beam, ordered workers back, then smeared mud over the split."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MINER_LAMP_CIRCLE"
msgstr "At a mine mouth in {region_name}, several miners sat around a dying lamp, none willing to say first what they had heard below."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_ORE_APPRAISER_BLUE_VEIN"
msgstr "An ore appraiser in {region_name} cracked open a green-veined stone, saw blue light flash, and immediately lowered the quoted price."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MOUNTAIN_PEDDLER_PASS_PRICE"
msgstr "A mountain peddler in {region_name} set out dried mushrooms and beast sinew, then raised the price after hearing of cultivators fighting ahead."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_GINSENG_GATHERER_OLD_ROOT"
msgstr "In {region_name}, a ginseng gatherer dug up an old root, saw its tendrils curl like tiny hands, and hurriedly buried it again."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_BEAST_KEEPER_RESTLESS_CAGES"
msgstr "In the spirit beast garden of {sect_name}, the keeper heard several young beasts whimper at once and hung an extra night-patrol tablet."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_FORGE_ARTISAN_COLD_ANVIL"
msgstr "Inside the forge of {sect_name}, an artisan found frost forming on the anvil and stored the half-made sword blank in an iron case."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_COOK_LATE_RICE"
msgstr "In the back kitchen of {sect_name}, the cook counted the meal tablets three times and found one unclaimed portion."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SWEEPER_CHILD_FALLEN_TALISMAN"
msgstr "Below the stone steps of {sect_name}, a sweeper child found a scorched talisman corner and tucked it into the broom handle."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_VASSAL_STEWARD_GIFT_BOXES"
msgstr "Outside the gate of {sect_name}, a vassal steward rearranged gift boxes into two lines, never daring to place the costliest one first."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_LETTER_SERVANT_RAIN_MESSAGE"
msgstr "As mountain rain fell hard at {sect_name}, a letter servant held a soaked bamboo tube and waited for the duty disciple's nod."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_INNKEEPER_AVATAR_ROOM"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} took lodging in {region_name}, the innkeeper changed the bedding and quietly moved the mortal guests next door downstairs."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_BLACKSMITH_AVATAR_WEAPON_GLANCE"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} passed the forge in {region_name}, the blacksmith saw spirit light on the weapon and pulled the apprentice back."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_ARTIFACT_SHOPKEEPER_AVATAR_BOW"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} entered the artifact shop in {region_name}, the keeper stepped around the counter to bow, and even the loudest assistant went quiet."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_TAX_COLLECTOR_AVATAR_SEAL"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} passed the tax post of {region_name}, the collector glanced at the official seal and pushed the inspection ledger to the bottom."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_CONSTABLE_AVATAR_EVIL_CASE"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} passed the case room in {region_name}, a constable turned a still-wet testimony face down and pretended to grind ink."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_POSTAL_COURIER_AVATAR_ROAD"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} traveled the post road of {region_name}, a courier led the horse aside and waited for the dust to settle before mounting again."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SHIP_CAPTAIN_AVATAR_BOARD"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} boarded a ferry at {region_name}, the ship captain pulled in the gangplank and warned the sailors not to ask where the guest was going."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PEARL_DIVER_AVATAR_TIDE"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} stopped by the tide line of {region_name}, a pearl diver stepped away and hid the basket of fresh shells behind the reef."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MINE_FOREMAN_AVATAR_TUNNEL"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} approached a mine tunnel in {region_name}, the foreman waved the workers to the wall, and even their coughs were stifled."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MOUNTAIN_PEDDLER_AVATAR_GOODS"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} stopped before a mountain-goods stall in {region_name}, the peddler pushed the mortal goods back and left only spirit-touched trinkets."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_BEAST_KEEPER_AVATAR_HUSH"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} walked past the spirit beast pens of {sect_name}, the keeper hurriedly gestured for silence, afraid the young beasts would cry out."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_FORGE_ARTISAN_AVATAR_PAUSE"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} passed the forge of {sect_name}, the artisan stopped hammering and slowly lowered the red-hot blank into a cold spring."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SECT_COOK_AVATAR_EXTRA_BOWL"
msgstr "As {avatar_name} passed the back kitchen of {sect_name}, the cook quietly ladled an extra bowl of spirit-rice porridge but did not dare invite them."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_SWEEPER_CHILD_AVATAR_BROOM"
msgstr "When {avatar_name} stepped onto the stone stairs of {sect_name}, the sweeper child held the broom across the chest and cleared the middle path."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_RELIEF_OFFICER_HELP_PEOPLE_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} aided the people of {region_name}, the relief officer recopied the porridge-shed register and deliberately left the first line blank."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_WEAPON_SHOPKEEPER_BUY_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} bought a weapon in {region_name}, the shopkeeper rehung the remaining blades and did not call for customers loudly for half a day."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_PAWNSHOP_SELL_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left the pawnshop in {region_name}, the appraiser locked the received item away and had the bookkeeper write less about its origin."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_BLACKSMITH_REFINE_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} refined an item in {region_name}, the blacksmith picked up a few cold ashes and found the fingertips tingling."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_ARTIFACT_SHOPKEEPER_CAST_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} cast a spell and left {region_name}, the artifact shopkeeper lowered the curtain and checked each small item in the cabinet."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HUNTER_HUNT_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} hunted in {region_name}, a hunter followed broken branches for a few steps, then dismantled every old trap."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_HERB_GATHERER_HARVEST_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} harvested in {region_name}, a herb gatherer crouched by the clearing and dared take only a few common herbs."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_MINER_MINE_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left the ore vein in {region_name}, miners covered the newly exposed pattern with cloth and waited for the foreman."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_INNKEEPER_REST_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} rested one night in {region_name}, the innkeeper left the room empty for three days and changed only the incense each day."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_POST_STATION_MOVE_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left the post station of {region_name}, the station master wiped the next-route tablet and quietly changed the night travel hour."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_BEAST_KEEPER_SECT_MISSION_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} completed a sect errand, the spirit beast keeper relocked an empty cage and quietly counted the young beasts again."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_FORGE_ARTISAN_SECT_MISSION_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} turned in a sect mission, the forge artisan bundled the remaining scraps and marked them \"awaiting reinspection.\""

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_CENSOR_RETAINER_GOVERN_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} handled government affairs in {region_name}, the censor's retainer folded the notes in half and delivered only the first part."

msgid "BACKGROUND_NPC_EVENT_NIGHT_WATCHMAN_PLUNDER_ECHO"
msgstr "After {avatar_name} left the night alleys of {region_name}, the watchman tucked the clapper under his arm and did not call the peace again."
